data.description: Experience the perfect mix of comfort and convenience in this 3 bedroom, 2 bath house located on a huge corner lot. Recently updated kitchen and a quiet cul-de-sac location make it your ideal family home.  You'll find plenty of space to relax and entertain with friends and family in the large living room. Take advantage of the corner lot with a great outdoor seating area for summer evenings.The house has been lovingly cared for, featuring modern updates and a neutral color scheme throughout. Create memories with your children in this quiet neighborhood with limited traffic. It's the perfect place to call home. ***This property qualifies for a VA loan assumption with an attractive 2.7% fixed interest rate. Take advantage of this unique opportunity for lower closing costs and competitive financing terms.*** Get in touch with us now to schedule an appointment!
